reviews.review_text:
- The first thing I notice, listening to the first set, is that the Dead are playing so well it's ridiculous. The second thing is that the crowd energy by the taper is really ugly. What are they booing during Rain? Amazing Row Jimmy, very slow, very intricate. Splendid singing tonight too.

Great all the way through. Excellent mix.

who's playing those horns on Eyes of the World? This is a nicely played show.  The sound quality is pretty good.

Does anyone know anything about the horns on Eyes of the World?
GREAT SHOW! This show kicks ass!
